{"tid":2312052,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"現有理論不能解釋！半人馬座恆星驚現超重元素！　學者：被「外星人傾倒核廢料」","createTime":"2020-12-04T14:12:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-09T05:48:05.000Z","uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5f7c9ba8f3dd0acb54343934522694ac3170e38a","tid":2312052,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T14:12:36.000Z","msg":"人類對外星人的存在始終不斷探索，美國賓夕法尼亞州立大學天體物理學者指出，在距<br />\n離地球355光年外的半人馬座有1顆恆星，其光譜顯示，它可能被外星人當成核廢料傾倒<br />\n場。<br />\n <br />\n據《Daily Galaxy》報導，半人馬座的「Przybylski」（HD 101065）恆星位於地球355<br />\n光年外，1961年被波蘭天文學家安東尼．普爾茲別爾斯基（Antoni Przybylski）首次捕<br />\n捉，今年則被發現它需費時200年才能完成1次自轉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2JzkzUR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2JzkzUR&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1wwEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=dadf3987\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2JzkzUR</a>"},{"pid":"f4a365aad147a6a6f5a8b590498f5040544c111b","tid":2312052,"uid":249979,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T14:21:28.000Z","msg":"咁做好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得地球人咁on9倒返落自己星球既海洋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83036e5b403bd82b99ad6ab1956687556bbb965f","tid":2312052,"uid":83102,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4a365aad147a6a6f5a8b590498f5040544c111b","tid":2312052,"uid":249979,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T14:21:28.000Z","msg":"咁做好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得地球人咁on9倒返落自己星球既海洋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T15:07:33.000Z","msg":"地球整到太空電梯都一定會將核廢料飛出太空<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac71bd7a9e969dcb7ab79365f0b152d441280bbb","tid":2312052,"uid":249979,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"83036e5b403bd82b99ad6ab1956687556bbb965f","tid":2312052,"uid":83102,"like":1,"dislike":1